The paper deals with control algorithms for trajectory tracking in nonlinear systems, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The use of event-based control is also a common topic in robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG), which could be relevant to this paper. Additionally, the paper discusses the design of ultimate bounds, which is a topic in control engineering (cs.CE) and can also be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for autonomous systems.
